Employees dressed up as the "Grandfather Frost" and the "Snow Maiden" pose during the opening of the "Fairy Tales Path" at the "Residence of Grandfather Frost" in Moscow, Russia, Nov. 18, 2020. A total of 65 sculptures inspired by Russian and foreign fairy tales are installed along the path. (Photo by Alexander Zemlianichenko Jr/Xinhua) 

